title: Amra Dujana- Tagore Duets With Kanika Banerjee | Bengali Songs Audio Jukebox
description:
KANIKA BANERJEE , a legendary artiste who sang numerous Tagore songs from which we have compiled 10 remarkable DUETS with other four legends like Hemanta Mukherjee, Suchitra Mitra, Dwijen Mukherjee & Shyamal Mitra for this special album. The 3rd song of this Juke Box AJI E ANANDA SANDHYA rendered by Kanika Banerjee and Suchitra Mitra is a live recording recorded from ABHINANDAN SANDHYA at Rabindra Sadan, 8th January 1980 where these two artistes were felicitated with GOLD DISCs by The Gramophone Co. of India Ltd  currently known as Saregama India Ltd..
